m/Google-Pixel-8a-Unlocked-Advanced/dp/B0CYQFJSRF/">购买连结</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/30/amazon-prime-day-tiktok-shop-promotion/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Amazon Prime Day 下月中举行   TikTok 一周前办促销活动抢饮头啖汤</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>智能手表</h2><p>Apple Watch Ultra（第一代）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250414" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/810jr81lisl_ac_sl150-520x580.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/810jr81lisl_ac_sl150-520x580.jpg 520w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/810jr81lisl_ac_sl150.jpg 808w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 520px" /></p><p>Apple Watch Ultra 具有防水功能，电池续航力达 36 小时，适合喜欢运动、探险的用家。原价约为 HKD 4,363.69，现减至 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="3895.32374">3,895.32</span> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Watch-Ultra-Cellular-Titanium/dp/B0C7PJTHVM?ref=dlx_deals_dg_dcl_B0C7PJTHVM_dt_sl14_1f">购买连结</a></p><h2>无线耳机／喇叭</h2><p>Echo Dot (5th Gen) with Echo Buds (2023 Release)</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250442" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/71ndb05ygel_ac_sl150-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/71ndb05ygel_ac_sl150-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/71ndb05ygel_ac_sl150.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/71ndb05ygel_ac_sl150-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>这是一个套装组合，有 Echo Dot（第 5 代）及 Echo Buds（2023 年版本）。用家可以利用 Echo Buds 无缝连接至任何兼容 Alexa 的装置，继续播放。原价约为 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="780.4563775">780.46</span> ，现减至 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="390.15012749999994">390.15</span> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Echo-Deep-Blue-Release-Black/dp/B0C3DPZ9LQ?ref=dlx_deals_dg_dcl_B0C3DPZ9LQ_dt_sl14_1f">购买连结</a></p><p>JBL Tune Flex 无线蓝牙耳机</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250413" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61joerbxerl_ac_sl150-627x580.jpg" alt="" width="627" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61joerbxerl_ac_sl150-627x580.jpg 627w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61joerbxerl_ac_sl150.jpg 973w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 627px" /></p><p>JBL Tune Flex 真无线蓝牙耳机电池续航力长达 32 小时，备有 IPX4 防水防汗功能，让用家可以在运动时享受音乐。原价约为 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="780.3046525">780.30</span> ，现减至 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="468.0266525">468.03</span> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/JBL-Tune-Flex-Wireless-Cancelling/dp/B0C1QNRGHC?ref=dlx_deals_dg_dcl_B0C1QNRGHC_dt_sl14_1f&amp;th=1">购买连结</a></p><h2>即影即有菲林</h2><p>Fujifilm Instax Mini Instant Film Value Pack &#8211; 120 Photos</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250480" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61gu1xu2wml_ac_sl115-667x580.jpg" alt="" width="667" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61gu1xu2wml_ac_sl115-667x580.jpg 667w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61gu1xu2wml_ac_sl115.jpg 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 667px" /></p><p>Fujifilm 即影即有菲林。原价约为 HKD 832.43，现减至 HKD <span class="DFlfde SwHCTb" data-precision="2" data-value="624.3419475">624.34</span> ，平均每张菲林大约 HKD 5.2。</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Fujifilm-Instax-Mini-Instant-Value/dp/B07NWRG5T4">购买连结</a></p><h2>家庭电器</h2><p>Instant Pot Duo Plus 9 合 1 压力煲</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image