rcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61yq2hurpl_ac_sl1400-576x580.jpg 576w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61yq2hurpl_ac_sl1400.jpg 894w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/61yq2hurpl_ac_sl1400-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 576px" /></p><p>Shark AI Ultra Voice Control Robot Vacuum 具有 Matrix Clean 功能，吸尘机械人可以侦测家中甚么地方有垃圾。另外有自动清空垃圾功能，底座可容纳 60 日份量的垃圾。用家可以使用 Amazon Alexa 或 Google Assistant 设定清洁计划，控制机械人在甚么时候吸尘。原价约为 HKD 4,675.46 ，现减至 HKD 2,302.40 。</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Shark-AV2511AE-Self-Empty-Capacity-Navigation/dp/B09T4YZGQR/?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ref_=dlx_deals_sc_dcl_img_dt&amp;pd_rd_w=hDJw3&amp;content-id=amzn1.sym.cb099553-8b1e-4ecd-bf9d-2789a0a6379a&amp;pf_rd_p=cb099553-8b1e-4ecd-bf9d-2789a0a6379a&amp;pf_rd_r=K7TJP1VZEH6TREBBJYE8&amp;pd_rd_wg=waqNx&amp;pd_rd_r=477d2d6f-78f5-4e13-ab30-6fd7ade6287e&amp;th=1">购买连结</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/30/amazon-prime-day-tiktok-shop-promotion/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Amazon Prime Day 下月中举行   TikTok 一周前办促销活动抢饮头啖汤</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/15/amazon-prime-day-2024/shop_guide/">【专题】Amazon Prime Day 2024 消费攻略　抵买 SSD + Pixel 手机</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
