ntent/uploads/2024/07/05_mr6550.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong><u>Nighthawk M6 (MR6150) 5G LTE </u></strong><strong><u>流动热点 WiFi 6 装置</u></strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">M6 采用 Qualcomm SDX62 5G 晶片，5G 上网速度可高达 2.5Gbps，亦能向下兼容 4G 讯号。M6 可支援 32 部装置同时上网，足以于外出旅游时为多人提供网络。M6 配有 2.4 吋彩色触控式屏幕，足以清晰显示一切所需资讯供用家观看，而且操作简单，初次使用都能够轻松使用。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">MR6150 现时有 86 折优惠，一件只需要 $6280（原价: $7380），并赠送 $300 电子超市现金券。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249908" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/06_mr6150-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/06_mr6150-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/06_mr6150-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">查询：NETGEAR 港澳区独家总代理 Winco (3619 8833)</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">销售店铺：<a href="https://bit.ly/3wQfCtA">https://bit.ly/3wQfCtA</a></p><p><b>相关文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/27/netgear-orbi-970-2/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】NETGEAR Orbi 970　旗舰级 Wi-Fi 7 + 覆盖范围可达一万呎</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/netgear-event-2024june/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 快闪优惠　买指定商品可半价换购智能相架</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/19/netgear-sales-event-2024-6/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 六月父亲节「智」Smart 优惠推介　买指定型号送电子礼券及便携餐具</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/15/netgear-july/wireless-home/">NETGEAR 七月优惠推介    Nighthawk WiFi 7 路由器 RS300 全新登场</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
